#HotFromTheAcademy — NATURE RECONNECTION Exhibition

Celebrating the 20th anniversary our Academies, we invite you to discover the creations of our @makeupforeveracademy students: this exhibition, entitled “Nature Reconnection", gathers 32 artworks coming from all over the world, available on a dedicated virtual platform.

Explore the creative process of a new generation of Makeup Artists through our first worldwide digital art exhibition.

Discover this immersing experience on #LINKINBIO and until the 22nd of May at @jardindacclimatation in Paris.

#makeupforever

#HotFromTheAcademy — NATURE RECONNECTION Exhibition

At MAKE UP FOR EVER, we see makeup as an art. For the 20th anniversary of our Academies, we invite you to immerse yourself into the first worldwide face and body digital art exhibition, exploring the imagination of a young generation of Makeup Artists.

Showcasing @makeupforeveracademy student’s creations, Nature Reconnection exhibition is out tomorrow. Stay tuned!

REVEAL YOURSELF: REVEAL YOUR PASSION

Passion is a powerful force that guides and inspires us.
@makeupforeveracademy students celebrated their own passion by creating looks with vibrant colors, striking contrasts, and intense expressions.
 
Join us from May 28 to June 22 at @jardin_dacclimatation in Paris to discover this year’s exhibition.
 
#MAKEUPFOREVERACADEMY #MAKEUPFOREVER

Meet your new obsession: Artist Color Crayons. 27 shades, inspired by our cult-faves Artist Color Pencil and HD Skin Palettes, offer you the perfect pops of color.
 
#MAKEUPFOREVER

Makeup artist @ines.yandoko shows how to use our new Artist Color Crayons to create a colorful spring look. 

The shades used: 424 Flaming Hot Red,126 Epic Pumpkin, 808 Boundless Berry, 282 Iconic Purple and 140 Sparkling Quartz.

#MAKEUPFOREVER

Unleash your inner artist with the new Artist Color Crayon our new multi-tasking crayon, perfect for mixing and matching shades or pairing with Artist Color Pencil and Super Boost Lip Gloss for enhanced looks

Meet our new creme multi-use stick that can be used on your face, eyes and lips. It will blend perfectly on your skin, allowing you to create natural or sophisticated looks.

REVEAL YOURSELF

Join us from May 28 to June 22 at @jardindacclimatation in Paris.
